snippet.textDisplay:
It’s been 3 years since I felt loved with her. Although it was one-sided, I had gotten a chance to confess before the day I came to the Netherlands. Anyway, she and her sister (her sister knew about my feelings for her) made me a clown; they were just having fun that night. 

Now it’s already been a painful 6 months in the Netherlands. I got to see her through my dream last night and broke out in tears after seeing her. When I woke up, I saw it was propose day today, and my pillow was wet.

Thanks to the Almighty for this amazing feeling. Long live love.
